profile:
When all others fail, call the geeks. We will figure it out or your money back!

Garage Door Geeks are dedicated to bringing you satisfaction. With over 10 years of experience, our skilled technicians offer exceptional service to help keep your door last you longer. Garage Door Geeks technicians are provided with the skills and parts needed to make your door run smoothly. We offer warranty on all work that our qualified technicians perform on your garage door, along with the parts installed.

Our warranty is unbeatable, with flexible plans to help your garage door hold together strong for longer. We have great deals that will bring your door into optimal working condition. With all repairs performed, we lubricate your door with the proper spray lubricant. Before leaving your home, we give you important information on how to properly maintain your door. Without the proper knowledge of garage door mechanics, a home owner can’t be expected to maintain a door. Our trained technicians give you a quick lesson on what are the key components and how to optimize the life of your garage door.
Why choose us

    Qualified technicians fully equipped with the knowledge and parts to repair your garage door
    Fast, friendly and affordable service, with exceptional punctuality making sure to work around your schedule

profile:
Few people realize the importance of a working garage door until it breaks down - garage doors are protection for you and your belongings. They house your car, your storage, and serve as an additional entrance to your home. For many they may feel like an afterthought, but they provide a great deal of security in a way that few other doors do.
Best Choice Garage Doors

At Best Choice Garage Doors, our goal is to help you with all of your garage door needs. We are available in Toronto and GTA and specialize in any and all garage door related services including:

    Installation – When you need a new and state of the art garage door installed, we can provide you with the perfect choice for the design of your home – one that will withstand the elements and provide you with the look and security you need.
    Repair – When your garage door breaks down for any reason, our service experts are available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. We will send our professionals directly to your home to get your garage door fixed so you can feel safe and secure again.

We also offer both residential and commercial services, and are available for all of your garage door projects both large and small. Our customer service is second to none, and we will be happy to supply you with the installation, repair, or replacement that you need. Call us today to learn more about what we have to offer.

profile:
Fix It Right Garage Doors has been in the industry for years, meaning that when it comes to experience within the GTA, we are your best bet. Our company is one of the most reputable, trusted names in garage door repairs and installations. We offer a variety of products, installing, replacing parts and repairing locally. Our technicians are capable of a number of repair and installation services such as: Residential and commercial garage door installations, garage repair and maintenance, fixing snapped or broken cables and installation of new motors. 

We operate on the basis of full transparency, meaning we will never mislead our customers in any way. Our only goal is to ensure your 100% satisfaction with our repair or installation services, which is why we offer a lifetime warranty on all services and offer complete diagnostics before undertaking any repairs or installations. We help you determine the correct course of action for your budget, home’s exterior, garage door and needs. profile:
The Direct Drive Technology offers a traveling motor that glides silently along a fixed chain.

Extremely durable and long lasting due to only one moving part. The motor of the garage door opener is located at the door instead of the back of the garage door opener, maximizing power and minimizing wear and tear.

Extremely quiet garage door opener with virtually no vibrations. Perfect for homes with living spaces above or near the garage. 

Maximum lifting force because the motor is directly attached to the door.

profile:
Here at Choice Garage Door Denver, we realize that you’ll find lots of garage door service companies in the Denver area to decide on. We appreciate the trust that the customers have placed in us for longer than ten years and are hoping to make your choice much easier through providing reasons for picking us:

Expertise
Our technicians are experts in their specific fields, each having numerous years or decades, of practical experience. We do not use sub-contractors for our garage door fixes, our qualified professionals are highly trained and licensed, as well as fully covered by insurance to safeguard you and your home. With experienced staff in each and every department – Sales, Installation, Service – you can rest assured that you’re in good hands.

Value
We may not necessarily offer you the lowest price out there, but the Great service you get more than makes up for any variation in price. Using only quality parts set up by our knowledgeable and licensed techs, you can be assured your garage door opener is going to be installed the right way the first time, by specialists in the field and supported by a company that will be around for the lifespan of your product.

Commitment to Safety
We fully understand the risks that are present around what is often the largest moving object in the home: your garage door. This is the reason we commit a great deal of time to training our technicians to perform adjustments while using the safest techniques in the industry creating the safest possible environment for our staff and your family.

Choice Garage Door Denver is a locally managed service, and our expert technicians are able to service and repair all brand names and styles of garage doors & residential gates. So, in case your garage door is broken, bent, off the tracks, or maybe too noisy our friendly staff is standing by ready to assist you today.
name: Choice Garage Door Denver
